ropebwt3-phg
============

This repository is a fork of ropebwt3 (https://github.com/lh3/ropebwt3),
distributed under the MIT License. It adds the `refmap` subcommand for placing
pangenome queries on a designated reference genome, together with supporting
documentation under docs/. All original source files and the upstream license
are retained unchanged.

